WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:22.031 --> 00:00:23.911
We'll always be friends.

00:01:46.115 --> 00:01:50.075
I heard that Master has fallen.

00:01:57.624 --> 00:02:00.864
Yeah. I know.

00:02:01.882 --> 00:02:04.882
I ended up helping Xehanort.

00:02:06.371 --> 00:02:10.811
Master was...going to destroy Ven.

00:02:11.959 --> 00:02:15.199
So, I only fought to protect him.

00:02:16.507 --> 00:02:20.067
But, it was all according to Xehanort's plan...

00:02:20.597 --> 00:02:25.717
You won't be able to fulfill the Master's hopes for you that way, Terra!

00:02:39.013 --> 00:02:44.653
Xehanort wants me to fight Vanitas in order to create the X-blade.

00:02:46.317 --> 00:02:53.717
Master said the X-blade is something that isn't meant to exist and tried to destroy me.

00:02:53.760 --> 00:02:55.400
The X-blade?

00:02:55.819 --> 00:03:00.179
I have no idea what this X-blade is...

00:03:00.187 --> 00:03:06.107
but, my heart's afraid of its creation.

00:03:08.352 --> 00:03:13.672
Don't worry. We won't let your heart be afraid.

00:03:16.141 --> 00:03:20.261
I might have to fight with Vanitas.

00:03:21.111 --> 00:03:24.271
If that happens...

00:03:24.286 --> 00:03:25.406
I mean if--

00:03:25.409 --> 00:03:28.729
We're friends connected by a special bond.

00:03:29.993 --> 00:03:31.993
I won't let anything happen to you.

00:03:39.707 --> 00:03:42.707
I'm asking you this just because we're friends.

00:03:44.994 --> 00:03:46.794
Please--

00:03:47.839 --> 00:03:49.319
--destroy me.

00:04:16.705 --> 00:04:18.745
Behold!

00:04:19.145 --> 00:04:27.785
These are the ruins left by the keyblade masters who once joined their hearts and power together.

00:04:27.819 --> 00:04:33.819
It was here that the battle between keyblades of light and darkness unfolded.

00:04:33.828 --> 00:04:37.228
They are the remains of the Keyblade Wars!

00:04:40.768 --> 00:04:49.008
Thousands of keyblade masters died here for the sake of one key.

00:04:49.638 --> 00:04:52.878
Now, I will take it for myself!

00:04:57.453 --> 00:04:59.853
The X-blade!

00:05:46.364 --> 00:05:47.364
Ven!

00:06:01.212 --> 00:06:02.292
Aqua!

00:06:05.624 --> 00:06:06.544
Terra!

00:06:24.362 --> 00:06:25.602
Ven!

00:06:58.988 --> 00:07:01.748
Ven! Are you alright?

